ch.epfl.lasec.mova
Class MovaSignature

java.lang.Object
  ch.epfl.lasec.mova.MovaSignature

public class MovaSignature
extends java.lang.Object

Class used to represent a Mova signature. A mova signature is described by

(Ysig1,...,YsigLsig)
which was computed from the message that was signed by
GenS(m) = (Xsig1,...,XsigLsig
and then for all i = 1 ,..., Lsig:
Ysigi = Hom(Xsigi).

Author:
Sebastien Duc
